ings before storage and should not add full transcript paths, working\ndirectories, branch names, or raw provider session ids as normalized fields.\n","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-20T17:16:22.314Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"[REDACTED:entropy]"}}}